    const A = {"tl":{"Fresh homemade Asian meals near you":"Sariwang lutong-bahay na Asian food malapit sa iyo","Warm":"Warm","Plum":"Plum","Spice":"Maanghang","Fresh":"Fresh","Minimal":"Minimal","Preview":"Preview","Promo poster":"Promo poster","Download":"Download","Max dishes":"Max dishes","Full Menu":"Full Menu","Print & Promo":"Print & Promo","QR code":"QR code","Menu posters":"Menu posters","Hero + Menu":"Hero + Menu","Promo Poster":"Promo Poster","Business Card":"Business Card","Thank You Card":"Thank You Card","Menu Poster":"Menu Poster","Styled":"Styled","Grid":"Grid","Text":"Text","Pro Print Kit":"Pro Print Kit","Variants":"Variants","Download PDF":"Download PDF","Download image":"Download image","Columns":"Columns","Columns:":"Columns:","1 column":"1 column","2 columns":"2 columns","Flow":"Flow","Balanced columns":"Balanced columns","Fill left first":"Unahin ang kaliwa","Across rows":"Pahalang sa rows","Soft Sand":"Soft Sand","Warm Beige":"Warm Beige","Midnight Mono":"Midnight Mono","Slate Blue":"Slate Blue","Berry Plum":"Berry Plum","Midnight Gold":"Midnight Gold","Styled Menu":"Styled Menu","Design":"Design","Image cards":"Image cards","Template":"Template","Card background":"Card background","Brand color":"Brand color","Business cards":"Business cards","Thank-you cards":"Thank-you cards","Text variant":"Text variant","Background":"Background","Main text":"Main text","Kitchen name":"Kitchen name","Pro tools":"Pro tools","Locked feature":"Locked feature","Tools":"Tools","Supplies":"Supplies","Print tools":"Print tools","Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"Tingnan muna ang promo poster bago i-download.","Number of dishes in menu posters":"Bilang ng dishes sa menu posters","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"Gamitin ang lahat ng dishes, o magtakda ng limit kung masyadong siksik ang layout. Apektado nito ang Full Menu at Hero + Menu.","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"Gamitin ang lahat ng dishes, o magtakda ng limit kung masyadong siksik ang layout. Ginagamit ito ng Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu at Hero + Menu.","Line + section heading color":"Kulay ng linya + section heading","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Gumagamit ang Full Menu ng bahagyang mas maliit na menu text at simpleng frame sa paligid ng menu area. Direktang nag-a-update ang kulay sa preview.","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"Pinakamainam para sa buong overview, internal use, pickup at display. Ipinapakita ang sections tulad ng Mains, Sides at Drinks.","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Kinokontrol ng accent color ang accent elements. Kinokontrol ng dark text + QR ang madidilim na bahagi, kasama ang QR code.","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"Pumili ng variant, tingnan agad ang poster, at buksan lang ang editing kapag kailangan.","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"Ilagay ang QR, posters at simpleng print files sa isang lugar. I-save muna ang changes sa Dashboard, pagkatapos i-download ang files dito.","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"Malinis na QR file para sa sharing, printing, business cards at local visibility.","See the QR file before you download it.":"Tingnan ang QR file bago i-download.","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"Menu poster set na may practical at customer-facing variants: Full Menu at Hero + Menu. Gamitin ang Max dishes kung masyadong siksik ang layout.","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"Pinapanatili ng hero image ang tamang proportions at hindi ito ini-stretch. Ikaw lang ang nagkokontrol kung aling bahagi ng image ang nasa frame, kasama ang zoom/position at colors sa preview.","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"Magandang middle ground: malaking hero image sa itaas at menu sa ibaba. Maganda kapag gusto mong pagsamahin ang branding at overview.","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"Tip: Gamitin ang Print & Promo para sa lahat ng gusto mong i-print, i-share locally, o isabit.","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"Pumili ng color variant o i-fine-tune manually. Direktang nag-a-update ang colors sa preview, at puwede mong i-save kapag okay na.","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"Parehong style ng Styled Menu, pero walang images at mas text-based tulad ng Full Menu. Pumili ng 1 o 2 columns.","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"Menu na may images. Pumili ng 1 o 2 columns. Sa 2-column mode, puwede ring piliin kung paano aayos ang dishes.","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"Ginagamit ng variant na ito ang parehong colors at variants gaya ng Styled Menu.","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"Mas magaan at mas designed na menu poster na gumagamit ng images mula sa menu at web-like layout.","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"Styled Menu na may live-editable colors.","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"Nag-a-update nang live ang card habang ina-adjust mo ito. I-save kapag satisfied ka na.","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"Printable sheet na may business cards at QR.","Business card image reset.":"Na-reset ang business card image.","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"Isang simpleng order insert na may QR at selectable message. Maganda itong ilagay sa bag para sa delivery o pickup.","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"Printable sheet na may thank-you cards para sa bag inserts.","Thank-you card reset.":"Na-reset ang thank-you card.","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"Tip: I-update ang name, contact details, menu at cover image sa Dashboard bago i-download ang print files.","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"Tumatakbo ang apps bilang separate browser tools. Lokal na nag-a-upload, nag-e-edit at nag-e-export ang user sa sariling device.","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Ang Print & Promo ay para sa kitchens na gusto ng QR, simpleng promo posters at menu posters para sa local marketing.","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"Mag-upgrade sa Business para magamit ang Print & Promo. Kasama rin sa Growth at Pro ang Pro Print Kit.","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Nagbibigay ang Pro Print Kit ng mas advanced na sales material kaysa Print & Promo.","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"Styled Menu na may mas premium na menu layout","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"Mas polished na visual style para sa flyers, menus at local promotion","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"May Print & Promo ka sa current plan. Mag-upgrade sa Growth para sa Pro Print Kit.","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"Mag-upgrade sa Growth para sa Print & Promo at Pro Print Kit.","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"I-save ang Styled Menu Text changes","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Na-save ang Styled Menu Text.","Reset Styled Menu Text":"I-reset ang Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Na-reset ang Styled Menu Text.","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"I-save ang Styled Menu Grid changes","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Na-save ang Styled Menu Grid.","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"I-reset ang Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Na-reset ang Styled Menu Grid.","Save Styled Menu changes":"I-save ang Styled Menu changes","Styled Menu saved.":"Na-save ang Styled Menu.","Reset Styled Menu":"I-reset ang Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Na-reset ang Styled Menu.","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · Salamat sa order mo / Welcome ulit","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · Sana magustuhan mo ang pagkain / Salamat sa support","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · Ginawa nang may pag-aalaga / Kita ulit soon","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · Salamat / Welcome bumalik anytime","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · Minimal / handwritten style"},"th":{"Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"ดูตัวอย่างโปสเตอร์โปรโมตก่อนดาวน์โหลด","Number of dishes in menu posters":"จำนวนเมนูในโปสเตอร์เมนู","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"ใช้ทุกเมนู หรือจำกัดจำนวนถ้าเลย์เอาต์แน่นเกินไป มีผลต่อ Full Menu และ Hero + Menu","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"ใช้ทุกเมนู หรือจำกัดจำนวนถ้าเลย์เอาต์แน่นเกินไป การตั้งค่านี้ใช้กับ Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu และ Hero + Menu","Line + section heading color":"สีเส้น + หัวข้อหมวด","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Full Menu ใช้ตัวอักษรเมนูเล็กลงเล็กน้อยและมีกรอบเรียบง่ายรอบพื้นที่เมนู สีจะอัปเดตในตัวอย่างทันที","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"เหมาะสำหรับภาพรวมทั้งหมด การใช้งานภายใน การรับอาหาร และการแสดงผล แสดงหมวดเมนูเช่น Mains, Sides และ Drinks","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Accent color ควบคุมองค์ประกอบเน้นสี Dark text + QR ควบคุมส่วนสีเข้ม รวมถึง QR code","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"เลือกแบบ ดูโปสเตอร์ได้ทันที และเปิดแก้ไขเฉพาะเมื่อจำเป็น","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"เก็บ QR โปสเตอร์ และไฟล์พิมพ์ง่ายๆ ไว้ที่เดียว บันทึกการเปลี่ยนแปลงใน Dashboard ก่อน แล้วดาวน์โหลดไฟล์ที่นี่","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"ไฟล์ QR ที่สะอาดสำหรับแชร์ พิมพ์ นามบัตร และการมองเห็นในพื้นที่","See the QR file before you download it.":"ดูไฟล์ QR ก่อนดาวน์โหลด","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"ชุดโปสเตอร์เมนูพร้อมแบบใช้งานจริงและแบบสำหรับลูกค้า: Full Menu และ Hero + Menu ใช้ Max dishes ถ้าเลย์เอาต์แน่นเกินไป","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"ภาพ hero จะรักษาสัดส่วนที่ถูกต้องและไม่ถูกยืด คุณควบคุมเฉพาะส่วนของภาพในกรอบ รวมถึง zoom/position และสีในตัวอย่าง","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"ทางเลือกกลางที่ดี: ภาพ hero ใหญ่ด้านบนและเมนูด้านล่าง เหมาะเมื่ออยากรวมแบรนด์กับภาพรวม","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"เคล็ดลับ: ใช้ Print & Promo สำหรับสิ่งที่ต้องการพิมพ์ แชร์ในพื้นที่ หรือแขวนแสดง","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"เลือกแบบสีหรือปรับเอง สีจะอัปเดตในตัวอย่างทันที และบันทึกเมื่อพอใจ","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"สไตล์เดียวกับ Styled Menu แต่ไม่มีรูปภาพ และเป็นเลย์เอาต์ข้อความคล้าย Full Menu เลือก 1 หรือ 2 คอลัมน์","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"เมนูพร้อมรูปภาพ เลือก 1 หรือ 2 คอลัมน์ ในโหมด 2 คอลัมน์ เลือกการไหลของเมนูได้ด้วย","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"แบบนี้ใช้สีและตัวเลือกเดียวกับ Styled Menu","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"โปสเตอร์เมนูที่เบาและออกแบบมากขึ้น ใช้รูปจากเมนูและเลย์เอาต์แบบเว็บ","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"Styled Menu ที่แก้ไขสีแบบ live ได้","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"การ์ดนี้จะอัปเดตทันทีระหว่างปรับ บันทึกเมื่อพอใจ","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"แผ่นพิมพ์พร้อมนามบัตรและ QR","Business card image reset.":"รีเซ็ตรูปนามบัตรแล้ว","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"ใบแทรกออเดอร์แบบง่ายพร้อม QR และข้อความที่เลือกได้ เหมาะสำหรับใส่ในถุง delivery หรือ pickup","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"แผ่นพิมพ์พร้อมการ์ดขอบคุณสำหรับใส่ในถุง","Thank-you card reset.":"รีเซ็ตการ์ดขอบคุณแล้ว","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"เคล็ดลับ: อัปเดตชื่อ ข้อมูลติดต่อ เมนู และภาพปกใน Dashboard ก่อนดาวน์โหลดไฟล์พิมพ์","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"แอปทำงานเป็นเครื่องมือแยกในเบราว์เซอร์ ผู้ใช้อัปโหลด แก้ไข และส่งออกไฟล์ในอุปกรณ์ของตนเอง","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Print & Promo สำหรับครัวที่ต้องการ QR โปสเตอร์โปรโมตง่ายๆ และโปสเตอร์เมนูสำหรับการตลาดในพื้นที่","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"อัปเกรดเป็น Business เพื่อใช้ Print & Promo ส่วน Growth และ Pro รวม Pro Print Kit ด้วย","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Pro Print Kit ให้สื่อขายที่ก้าวหน้ากว่า Print & Promo","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"Styled Menu พร้อมเลย์เอาต์เมนูระดับพรีเมียมกว่า","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"สไตล์ภาพที่ขัดเกลามากขึ้นสำหรับ flyer เมนู และการโปรโมตในพื้นที่","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"แพ็กเกจปัจจุบันของคุณมี Print & Promo อัปเกรดเป็น Growth เพื่อใช้ Pro Print Kit","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"อัปเกรดเป็น Growth เพื่อใช้ทั้ง Print & Promo และ Pro Print Kit","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"บันทึก Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Styled Menu Text บันทึกแล้ว","Reset Styled Menu Text":"รีเซ็ต Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Styled Menu Text รีเซ็ตแล้ว","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"บันทึก Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Styled Menu Grid บันทึกแล้ว","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"รีเซ็ต Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Styled Menu Grid รีเซ็ตแล้ว","Save Styled Menu changes":"บันทึก Styled Menu","Styled Menu saved.":"Styled Menu บันทึกแล้ว","Reset Styled Menu":"รีเซ็ต Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Styled Menu รีเซ็ตแล้ว","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · ขอบคุณสำหรับออเดอร์ / ยินดีต้อนรับอีกครั้ง","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · ขอให้อร่อย / ขอบคุณที่สนับสนุน","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · ทำด้วยความใส่ใจ / แล้วพบกันใหม่","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · ขอบคุณ / กลับมาได้ทุกเมื่อ","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · มินิมอล / สไตล์ลายมือ"},"vi":{"Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"Xem trước poster khuyến mãi trước khi tải xuống.","Number of dishes in menu posters":"Số món trong poster menu","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"Dùng tất cả món, hoặc đặt giới hạn nếu bố cục quá dày. Áp dụng cho Full Menu và Hero + Menu.","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"Dùng tất cả món, hoặc đặt giới hạn nếu bố cục quá dày. Cài đặt này dùng cho Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu và Hero + Menu.","Line + section heading color":"Màu đường kẻ + tiêu đề phần","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Full Menu dùng chữ menu nhỏ hơn một chút và khung đơn giản quanh khu vực menu. Màu cập nhật trực tiếp trong bản xem trước.","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"Phù hợp cho tổng quan, dùng nội bộ, pickup và trưng bày. Hiển thị các phần như Mains, Sides và Drinks.","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Accent color điều khiển các phần nhấn màu. Dark text + QR điều khiển các phần tối, gồm cả QR code.","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"Chọn một phiên bản, xem poster ngay và chỉ mở chỉnh sửa khi cần.","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"Giữ QR, poster và file in đơn giản ở một nơi. Lưu thay đổi trong Dashboard trước, rồi tải file tại đây.","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"File QR rõ ràng để chia sẻ, in, dùng trên danh thiếp và tăng hiển thị địa phương.","See the QR file before you download it.":"Xem file QR trước khi tải xuống.","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"Bộ poster menu với phiên bản thực tế và hướng tới khách hàng: Full Menu và Hero + Menu. Dùng Max dishes nếu bố cục quá dày.","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"Ảnh hero giữ đúng tỉ lệ và không bị kéo giãn. Bạn chỉ điều chỉnh phần ảnh nằm trong khung, cùng zoom/vị trí và màu ngay trong bản xem trước.","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"Lựa chọn cân bằng: ảnh hero lớn phía trên và menu bên dưới. Phù hợp khi muốn kết hợp thương hiệu và tổng quan.","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"Mẹo: Dùng Print & Promo cho mọi thứ bạn muốn in, chia sẻ tại địa phương hoặc treo lên.","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"Chọn biến thể màu hoặc tinh chỉnh thủ công. Màu cập nhật trực tiếp trong bản xem trước và bạn có thể lưu khi hài lòng.","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"Cùng phong cách với Styled Menu nhưng không có ảnh, bố cục chữ giống Full Menu hơn. Chọn 1 hoặc 2 cột.","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"Menu có ảnh. Chọn 1 hoặc 2 cột. Ở chế độ 2 cột, bạn cũng có thể chọn cách các món chảy theo bố cục.","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"Phiên bản này dùng cùng màu và biến thể như Styled Menu.","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"Poster menu nhẹ và có thiết kế hơn, dùng ảnh từ menu và bố cục giống web.","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"Styled Menu với màu có thể chỉnh trực tiếp.","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"Thẻ này cập nhật trực tiếp khi bạn điều chỉnh. Lưu khi bạn hài lòng.","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"Tờ in với danh thiếp và QR.","Business card image reset.":"Đã đặt lại ảnh danh thiếp.","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"Một tờ chèn đơn hàng đơn giản với QR và thông điệp có thể chọn. Phù hợp để đặt trong túi giao hàng hoặc pickup.","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"Tờ in với thẻ cảm ơn để đặt trong túi.","Thank-you card reset.":"Đã đặt lại thẻ cảm ơn.","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"Mẹo: Cập nhật tên, thông tin liên hệ, menu và ảnh bìa trong Dashboard trước khi tải file in.","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"Các app chạy như công cụ trình duyệt riêng. Người dùng tải file, chỉnh sửa và xuất về thiết bị của mình ở chế độ local.","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Print & Promo dành cho bếp muốn có QR, poster promo đơn giản và poster menu cho marketing địa phương.","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"Nâng cấp lên Business để dùng Print & Promo. Growth và Pro cũng bao gồm Pro Print Kit.","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Pro Print Kit cung cấp tài liệu bán hàng nâng cao hơn Print & Promo.","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"Styled Menu với bố cục menu cao cấp hơn","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"Phong cách hình ảnh chỉn chu hơn cho flyer, menu và quảng bá địa phương","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"Gói hiện tại của bạn có Print & Promo. Nâng cấp lên Growth để dùng Pro Print Kit.","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"Nâng cấp lên Growth để có cả Print & Promo và Pro Print Kit.","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"Lưu Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Styled Menu Text đã lưu.","Reset Styled Menu Text":"Đặt lại Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Styled Menu Text đã đặt lại.","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"Lưu Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Styled Menu Grid đã lưu.","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"Đặt lại Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Styled Menu Grid đã đặt lại.","Save Styled Menu changes":"Lưu Styled Menu","Styled Menu saved.":"Styled Menu đã lưu.","Reset Styled Menu":"Đặt lại Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Styled Menu đã đặt lại.","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · Cảm ơn đơn hàng của bạn / Hẹn gặp lại","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · Chúc bạn ngon miệng / Cảm ơn đã ủng hộ","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · Làm bằng sự chăm chút / Hẹn gặp lại sớm","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · Cảm ơn / Luôn chào đón bạn quay lại","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · Tối giản / phong cách viết tay"},"zh":{"Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"下载前先预览推广海报。","Number of dishes in menu posters":"菜单海报中的菜品数量","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"使用所有菜品，或在版面太拥挤时设置限制。这会影响 Full Menu 和 Hero + Menu。","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"使用所有菜品，或在版面太拥挤时设置限制。此设置用于 Styled Menu、Styled Menu Text、Full Menu 和 Hero + Menu。","Line + section heading color":"线条 + 分区标题颜色","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Full Menu 使用稍小的菜单文字，并在菜单区域周围加上简单边框。颜色会在预览中直接更新。","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"适合完整概览、内部使用、自取和展示。显示 Mains、Sides、Drinks 等菜单分区。","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Accent color 控制强调元素。Dark text + QR 控制深色元素，包括二维码。","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"选择一个版本，直接查看海报，只在需要时打开编辑。","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"将二维码、海报和简单打印文件集中在一个地方。先在 Dashboard 保存更改，然后在这里下载文件。","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"清晰的二维码文件，可用于分享、打印、名片和本地曝光。","See the QR file before you download it.":"下载前查看二维码文件。","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"菜单海报套装，包含实用版和面向客户的版本：Full Menu 和 Hero + Menu。如果版面太拥挤，请使用 Max dishes。","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"Hero 图片会保持正确比例，不会被拉伸。你只控制图片在框内显示的部分，以及预览中的缩放、位置和颜色。","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"很好的折中方案：顶部大 Hero 图，下方菜单。适合同时展示品牌和概览。","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"提示：凡是要打印、本地分享或张贴的内容，都可以使用 Print & Promo。","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"选择颜色版本或手动微调。颜色会在预览中直接更新，满意后即可保存。","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"与 Styled Menu 风格相同，但没有图片，文字布局更接近 Full Menu。可选 1 或 2 列。","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"带图片的菜单。可选 1 或 2 列。在 2 列模式下，也可选择菜品排列方式。","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"此版本使用与 Styled Menu 相同的颜色和变体。","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"更轻、更有设计感的菜单海报，使用菜单中的图片和类似网页的布局。","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"可实时编辑颜色的 Styled Menu。","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"此卡片会在你调整时实时更新。满意后保存。","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"包含名片和二维码的可打印页面。","Business card image reset.":"名片图片已重置。","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"简单订单插页，带二维码和可选信息。适合放入配送或自取袋中。","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"带感谢卡的可打印页面，可作为袋内插页。","Thank-you card reset.":"感谢卡已重置。","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"提示：下载打印文件前，请先在 Dashboard 更新名称、联系方式、菜单和封面图。","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"这些应用作为独立浏览器工具运行。用户在本地上传、编辑并导出到自己的设备。","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Print & Promo 适合需要二维码、简单推广海报和本地营销菜单海报的厨房。","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"升级到 Business 可使用 Print & Promo。Growth 和 Pro 也包含 Pro Print Kit。","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Pro Print Kit 提供比 Print & Promo 更高级的销售素材。","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"更高级菜单布局的 Styled Menu","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"适用于传单、菜单和本地推广的更精致视觉风格","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"你当前方案包含 Print & Promo。升级到 Growth 可使用 Pro Print Kit。","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"升级到 Growth 可同时使用 Print & Promo 和 Pro Print Kit。","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"保存 Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Styled Menu Text 已保存。","Reset Styled Menu Text":"重置 Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Styled Menu Text 已重置。","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"保存 Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Styled Menu Grid 已保存。","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"重置 Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Styled Menu Grid 已重置。","Save Styled Menu changes":"保存 Styled Menu","Styled Menu saved.":"Styled Menu 已保存。","Reset Styled Menu":"重置 Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Styled Menu 已重置。","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · 感谢您的订单 / 欢迎再次光临","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · 希望您喜欢这餐 / 感谢支持","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · 用心制作 / 期待再次见到您","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · 谢谢 / 随时欢迎回来","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · 极简 / 手写风格"},"id":{"Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"Pratinjau poster promo sebelum mengunduh.","Number of dishes in menu posters":"Jumlah hidangan di poster menu","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"Gunakan semua hidangan, atau batasi jika layout terlalu padat. Ini memengaruhi Full Menu dan Hero + Menu.","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"Gunakan semua hidangan, atau batasi jika layout terlalu padat. Pengaturan ini dipakai oleh Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, dan Hero + Menu.","Line + section heading color":"Warna garis + judul bagian","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Full Menu memakai teks menu sedikit lebih kecil dan bingkai sederhana di area menu. Warna langsung diperbarui di pratinjau.","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"Cocok untuk overview penuh, penggunaan internal, pickup, dan tampilan. Menampilkan bagian seperti Mains, Sides, dan Drinks.","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Accent color mengatur elemen aksen. Dark text + QR mengatur elemen gelap, termasuk QR code.","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"Pilih varian, lihat poster langsung, dan buka edit hanya saat perlu.","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"Simpan QR, poster, dan file cetak sederhana di satu tempat. Simpan perubahan di Dashboard dulu, lalu unduh file di sini.","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"File QR bersih untuk dibagikan, dicetak, kartu nama, dan visibilitas lokal.","See the QR file before you download it.":"Lihat file QR sebelum mengunduh.","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"Set poster menu dengan varian praktis dan untuk pelanggan: Full Menu dan Hero + Menu. Gunakan Max dishes jika layout terlalu padat.","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"Hero image menjaga proporsi yang benar dan tidak pernah diregangkan. Anda hanya mengatur bagian gambar di dalam frame, plus zoom/posisi dan warna langsung di pratinjau.","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"Pilihan tengah yang baik: hero image besar di atas dan menu di bawah. Cocok saat ingin menggabungkan branding dan overview.","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"Tip: Gunakan Print & Promo untuk semua yang ingin dicetak, dibagikan lokal, atau dipasang.","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"Pilih varian warna atau sesuaikan manual. Warna langsung diperbarui di pratinjau, dan Anda bisa menyimpan saat sudah puas.","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"Gaya yang sama seperti Styled Menu, tetapi tanpa gambar dan layout teks lebih mirip Full Menu. Pilih 1 atau 2 kolom.","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"Menu dengan gambar. Pilih 1 atau 2 kolom. Dalam mode 2 kolom, pengguna juga dapat memilih alur hidangan.","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"Varian ini memakai warna dan varian yang sama seperti Styled Menu.","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"Poster menu yang ringan dan lebih didesain, memakai gambar dari menu dengan layout seperti web.","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"Styled Menu dengan warna yang dapat diedit live.","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"Kartu yang ditampilkan di sini diperbarui langsung saat Anda menyesuaikan. Simpan saat sudah puas.","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"Lembar cetak dengan kartu nama dan QR.","Business card image reset.":"Gambar kartu nama direset.","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"Satu sisipan pesanan sederhana dengan QR dan pesan pilihan. Cocok dimasukkan ke tas untuk delivery atau pickup.","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"Lembar cetak dengan kartu terima kasih untuk sisipan tas.","Thank-you card reset.":"Kartu terima kasih direset.","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"Tip: Perbarui nama, detail kontak, menu, dan cover image di Dashboard sebelum mengunduh file cetak.","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"Aplikasi berjalan sebagai alat browser terpisah. Pengguna mengunggah file secara lokal, mengedit lokal, dan mengekspor ke perangkat sendiri.","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Print & Promo untuk dapur yang ingin QR, poster promo sederhana, dan poster menu untuk marketing lokal.","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"Upgrade ke Business untuk memakai Print & Promo. Growth dan Pro juga mencakup Pro Print Kit.","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Pro Print Kit memberi materi penjualan yang lebih lanjut daripada Print & Promo.","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"Styled Menu dengan layout menu yang lebih premium","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"Gaya visual yang lebih rapi untuk flyer, menu, dan promosi lokal","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"Plan Anda saat ini memiliki Print & Promo. Upgrade ke Growth untuk Pro Print Kit.","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"Upgrade ke Growth untuk Print & Promo dan Pro Print Kit.","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"Simpan Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Styled Menu Text disimpan.","Reset Styled Menu Text":"Reset Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Styled Menu Text direset.","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"Simpan Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Styled Menu Grid disimpan.","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"Reset Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Styled Menu Grid direset.","Save Styled Menu changes":"Simpan Styled Menu","Styled Menu saved.":"Styled Menu disimpan.","Reset Styled Menu":"Reset Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Styled Menu direset.","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · Terima kasih atas pesanan Anda / Selamat datang kembali","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · Semoga Anda menikmati makanannya / Terima kasih atas dukungannya","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · Dibuat dengan perhatian / Sampai jumpa lagi","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · Terima kasih / Selalu selamat datang kembali","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · Minimal / gaya tulisan tangan"},"ko":{"Preview the promo poster before downloading.":"다운로드 전에 홍보 포스터를 미리 보세요.","Number of dishes in menu posters":"메뉴 포스터의 메뉴 수","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This affects Full Menu and Hero + Menu.":"모든 메뉴를 사용하거나 레이아웃이 너무 빽빽하면 제한을 설정하세요. Full Menu와 Hero + Menu에 적용됩니다.","Use all dishes, or set a limit if the layout gets too dense. This setting is used by Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, and Hero + Menu.":"모든 메뉴를 사용하거나 너무 빽빽하면 제한을 설정하세요. 이 설정은 Styled Menu, Styled Menu Text, Full Menu, Hero + Menu에 사용됩니다.","Line + section heading color":"선 + 섹션 제목 색상","Full Menu uses slightly smaller menu text and a simple frame around the menu area. Colors update directly in the preview.":"Full Menu는 조금 작은 메뉴 글자와 메뉴 영역의 간단한 프레임을 사용합니다. 색상은 미리보기에서 바로 업데이트됩니다.","Best for full overview, internal use, pickup, and display. Shows menu sections like Mains, Sides, and Drinks.":"전체 개요, 내부 사용, 픽업 및 표시용으로 적합합니다. Mains, Sides, Drinks 같은 메뉴 섹션을 보여줍니다.","Accent color controls the accent elements. Dark text + QR controls the dark elements, including the QR code.":"Accent color는 강조 요소를 조정합니다. Dark text + QR은 QR 코드를 포함한 어두운 요소를 조정합니다.","Choose a variant, see the poster directly, and open editing only when you need it.":"버전을 선택하고 포스터를 바로 확인한 뒤 필요할 때만 편집을 여세요.","Keep your QR, posters, and simple print files in one place. Save changes in Dashboard first, then download the files here.":"QR, 포스터, 간단한 인쇄 파일을 한곳에 보관하세요. 먼저 Dashboard에서 변경사항을 저장한 뒤 여기서 파일을 다운로드하세요.","Clean QR file for sharing, printing, business cards, and local visibility.":"공유, 인쇄, 명함 및 지역 노출을 위한 깔끔한 QR 파일입니다.","See the QR file before you download it.":"다운로드 전에 QR 파일을 확인하세요.","Menu poster set with practical and customer-facing variants: Full Menu and Hero + Menu. Use Max dishes if the layout gets too dense.":"실용형과 고객용 변형이 포함된 메뉴 포스터 세트: Full Menu 및 Hero + Menu. 레이아웃이 너무 빽빽하면 Max dishes를 사용하세요.","The hero image keeps the correct proportions and is never stretched. You only control which part of the image sits inside the frame, plus zoom/position and colors directly in the preview.":"히어로 이미지는 올바른 비율을 유지하며 늘어나지 않습니다. 프레임 안에 보이는 부분과 zoom/position, 색상만 미리보기에서 조정합니다.","Great middle ground: large hero image at the top and the menu below. Good when you want to combine branding and overview.":"좋은 중간 선택: 위에는 큰 hero image, 아래에는 메뉴. 브랜딩과 개요를 함께 보여주고 싶을 때 좋습니다.","Tip: Use Print & Promo for everything you want to print, share locally, or hang up.":"팁: 인쇄, 지역 공유 또는 게시할 모든 자료에 Print & Promo를 사용하세요.","Choose a color variant or fine-tune manually. Colors update directly in the preview, and you can save when you are happy.":"색상 버전을 선택하거나 수동으로 조정하세요. 색상은 미리보기에서 바로 업데이트되며 만족하면 저장할 수 있습니다.","The same style as Styled Menu, but without images and with a text layout more like Full Menu. Choose 1 or 2 columns.":"Styled Menu와 같은 스타일이지만 이미지 없이 Full Menu에 가까운 텍스트 레이아웃입니다. 1열 또는 2열을 선택하세요.","Menu with images. Choose 1 or 2 columns. In 2-column mode, the user can also choose how dishes should flow.":"이미지가 있는 메뉴입니다. 1열 또는 2열을 선택하세요. 2열 모드에서는 메뉴 흐름도 선택할 수 있습니다.","This variant uses the same colors and variants as Styled Menu.":"이 버전은 Styled Menu와 같은 색상 및 변형을 사용합니다.","Light, more designed menu poster with images pulled from the menu and a web-like layout.":"메뉴 이미지와 웹 스타일 레이아웃을 사용하는 가볍고 더 디자인된 메뉴 포스터입니다.","Styled Menu with live-editable colors.":"색상을 실시간으로 편집할 수 있는 Styled Menu.","The card shown here updates live while you adjust it. Save when you are satisfied.":"여기 보이는 카드는 조정하는 동안 실시간으로 업데이트됩니다. 만족하면 저장하세요.","Printable sheet with business cards and QR.":"명함과 QR이 포함된 인쇄용 시트입니다.","Business card image reset.":"명함 이미지가 초기화되었습니다.","One simple order insert with QR and a selectable message. Good to place in the bag for delivery or pickup.":"QR과 선택 가능한 메시지가 있는 간단한 주문 안내 카드입니다. 배달 또는 픽업 봉투에 넣기 좋습니다.","Printable sheet with thank-you cards for bag inserts.":"봉투 삽입용 감사 카드 인쇄 시트입니다.","Thank-you card reset.":"감사 카드가 초기화되었습니다.","Tip: Update your name, contact details, menu, and cover image in Dashboard before downloading the print files.":"팁: 인쇄 파일을 다운로드하기 전에 Dashboard에서 이름, 연락처, 메뉴, 커버 이미지를 업데이트하세요.","The apps run as separate browser tools. The user uploads files locally, edits locally and exports to their own device.":"앱은 별도의 브라우저 도구로 실행됩니다. 사용자는 파일을 로컬에서 업로드하고 편집한 뒤 자신의 기기로 내보냅니다.","Print & Promo is for kitchens that want QR, simple promo posters and menu posters for local marketing.":"Print & Promo는 지역 마케팅용 QR, 간단한 홍보 포스터, 메뉴 포스터가 필요한 주방을 위한 기능입니다.","Upgrade to Business to use Print & Promo. Growth and Pro also include Pro Print Kit.":"Print & Promo를 사용하려면 Business로 업그레이드하세요. Growth와 Pro에는 Pro Print Kit도 포함됩니다.","Pro Print Kit gives you more advanced sales material than Print & Promo.":"Pro Print Kit는 Print & Promo보다 더 고급 판매 자료를 제공합니다.","Styled Menu with a more premium menu layout":"더 프리미엄한 메뉴 레이아웃의 Styled Menu","A more polished visual style for flyers, menus and local promotion":"전단지, 메뉴, 지역 홍보를 위한 더 세련된 시각 스타일","You have Print & Promo on your current plan. Upgrade to Growth for Pro Print Kit.":"현재 요금제에는 Print & Promo가 포함되어 있습니다. Pro Print Kit를 사용하려면 Growth로 업그레이드하세요.","Upgrade to Growth for both Print & Promo and Pro Print Kit.":"Print & Promo와 Pro Print Kit를 모두 사용하려면 Growth로 업그레이드하세요.","Save Styled Menu Text changes":"저장 Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text saved.":"Styled Menu Text 저장되었습니다.","Reset Styled Menu Text":"초기화 Styled Menu Text","Styled Menu Text reset.":"Styled Menu Text 초기화되었습니다.","Save Styled Menu Grid changes":"저장 Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid saved.":"Styled Menu Grid 저장되었습니다.","Reset Styled Menu Grid":"초기화 Styled Menu Grid","Styled Menu Grid reset.":"Styled Menu Grid 초기화되었습니다.","Save Styled Menu changes":"저장 Styled Menu","Styled Menu saved.":"Styled Menu 저장되었습니다.","Reset Styled Menu":"초기화 Styled Menu","Styled Menu reset.":"Styled Menu 초기화되었습니다.","1 · Thank you for your order / Welcome again":"1 · 주문해 주셔서 감사합니다 / 또 방문해 주세요","2 · Hope you enjoy your meal / Thanks for the support":"2 · 맛있게 드세요 / 응원해 주셔서 감사합니다","3 · Made with care / See you again soon":"3 · 정성껏 만들었습니다 / 곧 다시 만나요","4 · Thank you / Welcome back anytime":"4 · 감사합니다 / 언제든 다시 방문해 주세요","5 · Minimal / handwritten style":"5 · 미니멀 / 손글씨 스타일"}};


